<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You for Your Interest - Event-Driven PoC</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            margin: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .header p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        .highlight {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e3f2fd 0%, #f3e5f5 100%);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
        }
        .highlight h3 {
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .detail-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .detail-list li {
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .detail-list li:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #555;
        }
        .detail-value {
            color: #333;
            text-align: right;
            max-width: 60%;
            word-break: break-word;
        }
        .message-box {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #495057;
        }
        .next-steps {
            background: #e8f5e8;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .correlation-id {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-family: 'Monaco', 'Menlo', 'Ubuntu Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6c757d;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        .footer .team-name {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #495057;
        }
        .footer .disclaimer {
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .logo {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 10px;
            }
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .detail-list li {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }
            .detail-value {
                text-align: left;
                max-width: 100%;
                margin-top: 5px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">âš¡</div>
            <h1>Thank You, {{name}}!</h1>
            <p>We've received your message and will get back to you soon.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p class="greeting">Dear {{full_name}},</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for reaching out to us through our contact form. We appreciate your interest in our event-driven architecture solutions and the time you took to share your requirements with us.</p>
            
            <div class="highlight">
                <h3>ðŸ“‹ Your Submission Details</h3>
                <ul class="detail-list">
                    <li>
                        <span class="detail-label">Company:</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">{{company}}</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="detail-label">Email:</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">{{email}}</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="detail-label">Phone:</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">{{phone}}</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="detail-label">Preferred Contact:</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">{{preferred_contact_method}}</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="detail-label">Submitted:</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">{{submission_date}} at {{submission_time}}</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <h3>ðŸ’¬ Your Message:</h3>
            <div class="message-box">
                {{message}}
            </div>
            
            <div class="next-steps">
                <h3>ðŸš€ What Happens Next?</h3>
                <p>Our technical team will review your inquiry and respond within <strong>24 hours</strong>. We'll reach out via your preferred contact method to discuss how our event-driven architecture solutions can help your organization.</p>
            </div>
            
            <p>In the meantime, feel free to explore our documentation and examples to learn more about the capabilities of our platform.</p>
            
            <div class="correlation-id">
                <strong>System Reference:</strong> {{correlation_id}}<br>
                <small>This email was generated automatically by our event-driven system</small>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p class="team-name">Best regards,<br>The Event-Driven Architecture Team</p>
            <p class="disclaimer">This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

